# ============================================================
# NAME:    CQG
# TYPE:    Data Source (market data + order-routing gateways)
# REPO:    https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# UPDATED: 2026-07-08
# USED BY: NinjaTrader (Continuum), SierraChart, ATAS
# EXIT:    Route CQG to the SAME exit as the platform using it (NinjaTrader/ATAS/SierraChart),
#          otherwise the program and its data feed land in different regions -> login fails / data lag.
# NOTE:    LAN trading PCs proxy through Surge, so PROCESS-NAME does NOT apply to them.
#          Routing relies entirely on the DOMAIN / IP rules below.
# SOURCE:  NinjaTrader Continuum/CQG live gateways sit in Chicago, Hong Kong, Singapore, Tokyo, Sydney, London.
# SOURCE:  CQG technical specs list CQG Trader / IMS / data / news host suffixes.
# ============================================================

# ---- CQG host suffixes (cover all sub-hosts, incl. regional gateways) ----
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cqg.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cqgtrader.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cqgnet.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cqgrdnet.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cqgdata.com

# ---- Regional gateways (already covered by the suffixes above; kept for reference) ----
# europe.cqgtrader.com  (Europe)
# sng.cqgtrader.com     (Singapore)
# au.cqgtrader.com      (Australia)
# tokyo.cqgtrader.com   (Tokyo)
# api-hongkong.cqg.com  (Hong Kong)

# ---- CQG stable gateway IPs (no-resolve: match by dest IP, skip DNS) ----
IP-CIDR,208.48.16.200/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,209.8.147.53/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,216.219.76.110/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,118.201.11.201/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,203.192.64.137/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,114.31.92.73/32,no-resolve

